headline: Does Seagate’s 148% Rally Reflect Its Real Value After Latest AI Storage Demand Surge?
summary: Trying to figure out what to do with Seagate Technology Holdings stock right now? You’re not alone. With the stock closing at $214.38 and rocketing up 148.2% since the start of the year, it’s no wonder this company is on everyone’s radar. Of course, the ride hasn't been all smooth. Over the past week, Seagate dipped by 15.2%, showing just how quickly sentiment or risk perceptions can change in this market.
